text: The Living Corpse () is a 1929 German-Soviet silent drama movie directed by Fyodor Otsep.Убийцы выходят на дорогуБиблиотека киноискусства приглашает на показы It stars Vsevolod Pudovkin, Maria Jacobini, and Viola Garden. ==Actors== * Vsevolod Pudovkin as Fyodor Protasov * Maria Jacobini as Yelizaveta Andreyevna Protasova (Liza) * Viola Garden as Sasha (Liza's sister) * Julia Serda as Anna Pavlovna * Nato Vachnadze as Masha, a gypsy * Gustav Diessl as Viktor Mikhajlovich Karenin == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Russian silent movies Category:Russian drama movies Category:1929 drama movies Category:German silent movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by Fyodor Otsep Category:Soviet silent movies Category:Soviet drama movies
